info.name: Disneyland Typography
info.description: Tumblr logo comprised of the T from the entrance to Tomorrowland, the U from the Haunted Mansion plaque, the M from the Matterhorn, the B from Big Thunder, an L from It's a Small World, and the R from the Enchanted Tiki Room. Replaces the standard "tumblr." logo on your dashboard.

style.css: @namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml); @-moz-document url-prefix('https://www.tumblr.com/'), url-prefix('http://www.tumblr.com/')   { #logo {height: 0 !important; width: 0 !important; padding-left: 350px !important; padding-top: 44px !important; background: url(http://24.media.tumblr.com/b359ae200087fe61db6d99e859618fd2/tumblr_mri4t7h3PJ1rgoq1io1_250.png) no-repeat !important;}}
